<h5>Are you at the cross-roads to choose your career path between
Technology and Management?</h5>
<h3>What if you had the chance to excel in both
the domains?</h3>
<p>Indian Institute of Technology, Madras (IITM) and Indian Institute of Management, Bangalore
(IIMB) have been front runners in providing quality education in their respective domains for
several years. <strong>Robert Bosch Centre for Data Science and AI, IIT Madras and IIMBx, IIM
  Bangalore</strong> have now collaborated to provide a <strong>Certificate Programme in "Technology
    and Management" (CTM)</strong> to transform your career to the next level.</p>

    <p>The 11 month programme will comprise technical courses from IIT Madras and management
courses from IIM Bangalore. Besides learning the core management courses, the students
will have an opportunity to choose one of the two technical disciplines offered, namely Data
Sciences and Machine Learning.</p>

<p>This collaborative online programme brings together an active learning blend of Technology
and Management, by imparting knowledge about the current market trends in both the
streams. It empowers you with a unique cross-functional skillset essential to cater to the
emerging business needs.</p>
<p>In addition, you will experience the IIT Madras and IIM Bangalore classrooms through
campus connect sessions, where you will have opportunities to interact with the faculty for
case study and project discussions.</p>
<p>On successful completion of the programme, the learners receive a Certificate in Technology
and Management.</p>
<p>The programme is scheduled to begin in March 2019. Registrations are open.</p>
<p>Broaden your horizon and equip yourself with the best in-class certification.
To know more and apply, visit <a href="https://ctm-iitm.iimbx.edu.in/"> https://ctm-iitm.iimbx.edu.in/</a></p>
